---
layout: layouts/component-demo.njk
title: Toggle Button
description: a button that toggles between pressed and unpressed states
---

{% from "components/toggle-button/macro.njk" import toggleButton %}

<h2>Default (unpressed)</h2>
<p>{{ toggleButton({ text: "Bold" }) }}</p>

<h2>Pressed</h2>
<p>{{ toggleButton({ text: "Bold", pressed: true }) }}</p>

<h2>Use aria-pressed, not role=switch</h2>
<p>Use <code>ToggleButton</code> for "currently-applied formatting"
  or "action in effect" semantics (Bold, Italic, Mute). For explicit
  on/off settings, prefer <a href="/components/switch-button/">
  <code>SwitchButton</code></a> with its
  <code>role="switch"</code>.</p>
